				<div class="comment-content post-content" itemprop="text">
					<p>Thank you, during the incident that particular IP was connected to because one of the files was signed and that site was used to validate the certificate. You are correct that it was a mistake to class this as command and control. We have removed it to avoid confusion.</p>
